          <unittitle>Michigan Association for Media in Education</unittitle>
        </did>
        <scopecontent>
          <p>The Michigan Association for Media in Education material, the bulk of which was received in 2009, includes two principal sub-series: History and Conferences. Each of these is comprised of binders arranged by year. The History volumes include constitution and articles of incorporation; membership materials; board of directors minutes and financial material; records of organization officers, divisions, standing committees, and affiliates; and newsletters and various subject files. Each of the binders contains a detailed index. The Conference volumes relate to the yearly meeting of the organization and include agendas, programs, evaluations and related material. Other MAME materials include scrapbooks, publication of the organization, and miscellaneous sound cassettes and photographic slides.</p>
        </scopecontent>
